# Gemini PDF Study Assistant - Environment Configuration File
#
# This file contains template for environment variables needed to run the application.
#
# IMPORTANT:
# 1. Copy this file to .env (without .example)
# 2. Replace placeholder values with your actual credentials
# 3. NEVER commit the .env file to version control
# 4. Add .env to .gitignore
#
# How to get your Google (Gemini) API Key (FREE):
# 1. Go to https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# 2. Sign in with your Google account
# 3. Click "Create API key" and choose or create a project
# 4. Copy the key and paste it below
# 5. Keep this key secret - never share it publicly
#
# Example of a valid key (not real):
# GOOGLE_API_KEY=AIzaSy...

# Google (Gemini) API Key - Required for the application to work
# Type: String
# Cost: Free tier available via Google AI Studio
GOOGLE_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

# Optional: You can add more configuration variables here as your project grows
# For example:
# APP_ENV=development
# LOG_LEVEL=INFO
# MAX_PDF_SIZE=50  # in MB
# MAX_QUESTIONS_PER_SESSION=100
